86. PHP File functions with example program.
Some useful file functions:
•	fopen(), fclose(), fread(), fwrite()
•	file_exists(), filesize(), unlink()
•	file_get_contents(), file_put_contents()
<?php
$file = "test.txt";
// Writing
file_put_contents($file, "Hello World!\n", FILE_APPEND);
// Reading
if (file_exists($file)) {
    $data = file_get_contents($file);
    echo "File Content:<br>" . nl2br($data);
}
?>
